<h2>Bleeding, Blood in toilet and Worms in stool</h2>
<p>WebMD Symptom Checker helps you find the most common medical conditions indicated by the symptoms bleeding, blood in toilet and worms in stool including Pinworms, Ascaris worms, and Hemorrhoids.</p>
